OL,7,FA Jersey man has been found guilty of
OL,8,Fraping three young and vulnerable
OL,9,Fvictims who he deliberately targeted.
OL,11,FJersey's Royal Court heard 50-year-old
OL,12,FShay John Bester perpetrated his
OL,13,Fcrimes over many years, building his
OL,14,Fvictim's trust and then exerting
OL,15,Fcontrol over them through manipulation
OL,16,Fand coercion.
