OL,7,FHe committed the crimes against three
OL,8,Fyoung females between 1994 and 2007 -
OL,9,Fthe victims coming forward following
OL,10,FBester's separate conviction for
OL,11,Fgrooming a teenager online.
OL,13,FThe three cases began as separate
OL,14,Finvestigations, but were brought
OL,15,Ftogether when officers at the States
OL,16,Fof Jersey Police identified common
OL,17,Fpatterns.
