OL,7,FDC Elianne Jones, who led on the case
OL,8,Fsaid: "The victims in this case have
OL,9,Fshown exceptional bravery and
OL,10,Fresilience. Each has faced significant
OL,11,Fpersonal challenges in coming forward,
OL,12,Fand each has had to revisit deeply
OL,13,Ftraumatic experiences.
OL,15,F"The longterm impact of these
OL,16,Foffences has affected every aspect of
OL,17,Ftheir lives in different ways. It
OL,18,Frequired remarkable courage for all
OL,19,Fthree individuals to stand before the
OL,20,Fcourt and give their evidence, and we
OL,21,Fcommend them for their strength.
